metadata.name: Phetta
metadata.description:
Who is Phetta? Well, I guess you could say he is technically an embodiment of me. A creative alter ego. Look at me; I got an alter ego, okay! But really, Phetta is a curious and adventurous being constantly on the hunt to discover new ideas and create them into a reality of his own. But within the Phettaverse, he is a detective rat with a bold attitude and a rush for discovery. It can be all fun and games, but he's serious as a rock when it comes to his cases


This token is subject to change at any time.
